<reggrp_short_dscr>:
Access core memory
------------------------------
<reg_short_dscr>:
Core reset control
------------------------------
<reg_public_text>:
Controls reset and initialization of the switching core. Proper startup sequence is:
- Enable memories
- Initialize memories
- Enable core
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Initialize core memories. Field is automatically cleared when operation is complete (approx. 40 us).
